						<summary>

						<p>This is probably a Kannaḍa version of No. 256 above. It is much damaged and hence the gift portion is not clear except that a land was granted to the temple as <hi rend="italic">mānya</hi> for the requirements of worship to the deity. Mention is made of a person by name Tiruvēṅgaḍa••••</p>						

